Name: Stooker Roasting Company
Review Text: They have great donuts today, especially the speculoos one is certainly worth trying.

Name: Stooker Roasting Company
Review Text: Ordered a new grinder online. Kind and super helpfull. Shipping was fast and their coffees are delicious!

Name: Stooker Roasting Company
Review Text: One of the best specialty coffee place in Amsterdam. Today I had great coffees and great conversation about specialty coffee there. Thanks a lot Dann!

Name: Stooker Roasting Company
Review Text: Not really open to the public as a cafe. The coffee is very good and certainly worth trying. It can be literally twice the price as other decent coffees.

Name: Stooker Roasting Company
Review Text: Had a 'Stooker' coffee at the Legalloyd office: delicious!!! Keep up the good roasting work
